    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/c95faae13cc1ad1c9b821843f0d913ae.poster.avif?t=1690504351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/c95faae13cc1ad1c9b821843f0d913ae.webm?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/c95faae13cc1ad1c9b821843f0d913ae.mp4?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要</h2><strong>化身为身穿性感装束的女仆咖啡厅店长，横扫怪物的千军万马！</strong><br><br>可最多同时使用3样武器进行攻击、格档、做出连击打倒成群怪物。<br>找到头目的弱点并给予大量伤害吧。<br>操作简单但深奥的战斗系统与服装收集要素兼具的横向卷轴动作游戏！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><strong>女店员被哥布林集团给掳走了！</strong><br><br>为了夺回被掳走的店员，<strong>店长（巨乳）</strong>挺身而出。<br>究竟她是否能在这巨大昆虫、半兽人、甚至是龙等怪物嚣张跋扈的大地上杀出一条血路，成功救出店员呢？ <br>亦或者是，她也会惨遭毒手而落入恶人手里呢……？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >竞技场模式</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/beed91816f3a4ab113876fb15e5c0844.poster.avif?t=1690504351\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/beed91816f3a4ab113876fb15e5c0844.webm?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/beed91816f3a4ab113876fb15e5c0844.mp4?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通关过后会开放的竞技场模式可在六位角色中选择对手和服装并进行1对1的对战或4对4的乱斗，进行具挑战性的战斗。<br>充分运用每个角色独特的攻击方式、活用其优点和缺点，来取得战斗中的优势吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/f6bb5ff36d015c2bedafb9b56e857cc5.poster.avif?t=1690504351\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/f6bb5ff36d015c2bedafb9b56e857cc5.webm?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262990/extras/f6bb5ff36d015c2bedafb9b56e857cc5.mp4?t=1690504351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>变种大剑、斧、枪、机关枪、榴弹发射器、etc……共有9种独特的武器能让战斗方式千变万化!<br></li><li>女仆服、训练服、兔女郎装等等，3种特殊服装<br></li><li>狗、哥布林、半兽人、牛头人、蜘蛛、蚯蚓、青蛙、蜜蜂、龙等等，各种各样的敌人登场<br></li><li>游戏通关后可解锁竞技场模式，可使用战斗风格独树一格的次要角色们对战与游玩<br></li><li>4种需要不同战略的难易度<br></li><li>可自行调整的按键设定与支援手把，实现完全自订的游戏体验</li></ul>",
